<paragraph id="8BCE36F93C8AB78EFF4CFA2D7775FA0A" blockId="193.[178,1086,1436,1480]" pageId="193" pageNumber="806">
T y p u s m a t e r i a l: 
<typeStatus id="54CA885B3C8AB78EFE45FA2D7659FA72" box="[443,534,1436,1456]" pageId="193" pageNumber="806">Holotypus</typeStatus>
() und 1 - 
<typeStatus id="54CA885B3C8AB78EFD6CFA2D76A3FA72" box="[658,748,1436,1456]" pageId="193" pageNumber="806">Paratypus</typeStatus>
: 
<collectingCountry id="F36676693C8AB78EFD08FA2D7731FA72" box="[758,894,1436,1456]" name="Costa Rica" pageId="193" pageNumber="806">COSTA RICA</collectingCountry>
